{"tid":1168022,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"變態youtuber將熊仔鼠染成籃色 將鼠困在玻璃瓶","createTime":"2019-05-23T11:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T18:11:50.000Z","uid":271,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f9c3e02df3023d92a425b21f2749c7399ba2c87","tid":1168022,"uid":271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T11:52:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pFd3rEg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpFd3rEg.png&h=f96f81d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本有位自稱倉鼠愛好者的YouTuber，經營了一個名為「ハムハムTV」，上月底（4月27日），他在頻道上載了一段影片，標題指「發現了新品種倉鼠」。他稱自己很喜歡藍色，於是購入了一支寵物專用的染毛劑。影片裡，他把一隻倉鼠放在洗手盤裡，利用牙刷沾上藍色的染毛劑，並塗抹至牠身上。倉鼠在洗手盤不停逃走。他在影片中表示，染毛劑需停留在皮膚10至15分鐘，不過考慮到倉鼠的健康，只等待了5分鐘便為牠沖水，結果把染成了粉藍色。<br />\n<br />\n事隔兩週，他本月初（5月6日）再次在YouTube上載一段影片，內容指上次染色並不均勻，因此再度為牠染色。這次他染毛的手法變得非常熟練，更戴上手套，避免雙手沾上染毛劑，染毛劑停留的時間亦延長至10分鐘，結果「成功」把倉鼠染成鮮藍色。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">並非第一次虐待動物</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zLh4a6y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzLh4a6y.png&h=51b0838d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這位YouTuber並非第一次虐待寵物，他早前上載了另一段影片，指倉鼠偷偷咬破糧食，他竟然把鼠困進一個細小的玻璃瓶，並關上了瓶蓋，只在瓶蓋上開洞讓倉鼠能維持呼吸。倉鼠好幾度把鼻子伸出瓶蓋，瓶內的氧氣明顯不足，後來他把瓶子打直放，倉鼠無法再把鼻子伸到瓶外呼吸，牠慢慢虛弱地蓋上眼睛，他才把玻璃瓶打開。<br />\n<br />\n再者，他亦曾經強迫倉鼠進食「唐辛子」辣椒製成的零食，測試牠的反應，甚至故意利用指甲鉗為倉鼠剪牙。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌 睇到好嬲 去搞個隻熊仔鼠同我養緊果隻仲要好似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534235da774b3c314e5b03b188bc0c1b204c8286","tid":1168022,"uid":271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T11:53:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9/330809/youtuber%E8%87%AA%E7%A8%B1%E5%80%89%E9%BC%A0%E6%84%9B%E5%A5%BD%E8%80%85-%E6%8A%8A%E6%84%9B%E5%AF%B5%E6%9F%93%E6%88%90%E8%97%8D%E8%89%B2%E9%81%AD%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%82%AE%E8%BD%9F?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=anistoryhk&amp;fbclid=IwAR3viLzi_wmVmHiUqcOD889LdNlWpqLEb-iLBdr-yqJEzy4Fuv2z5acsKYE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%25AF%25B5%25E7%2589%25A9%2F330809%2Fyoutuber%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E5%2580%2589%25E9%25BC%25A0%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E8%2580%2585-%25E6%258A%258A%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%25AF%25B5%25E6%259F%2593%25E6%2588%2590%25E8%2597%258D%25E8%2589%25B2%25E9%2581%25AD%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2582%25AE%25E8%25BD%259F%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Danistoryhk%26fbclid%3DIwAR3viLzi_wmVmHiUqcOD889LdNlWpqLEb-iLBdr-yqJEzy4Fuv2z5acsKYE&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=17abeb0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%AF%B5%E7%89%A9/330809/youtuber%E8%87%AA%E7%A8%B1%E5%80%89%E9%BC%A0%E6%84%9B%E5%A5%BD%E8%80%85-%E6%8A%8A%E6%84%9B%E5%AF%B5%E6%9F%93%E6%88%90%E8%97%8D%E8%89%B2%E9%81%AD%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E7%82%AE%E8%BD%9F?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=anistoryhk&amp;fbclid=IwAR3viLzi_wmVmHiUqcOD889LdNlWpqLEb-iLBdr-yqJEzy4Fuv2z5acsKYE</a>"},{"pid":"32b63558a6a2aca6fd3d9b138f659b62aa0858c0","tid":1168022,"uid":19981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T11:53:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7880401831271e6696a5c5f361c2ca2d57dbc13","tid":1168022,"uid":271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T11:54:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCF5-r6zIT5vOTpDX0NeQpPQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCF5-r6zIT5vOTpDX0NeQpPQ&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=b528c426\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">